<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>My First Webpage</title>
<style>
  body{
    margin:0;
    font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;
    background:#fdfdfd;
    text-align:center;
    padding:50px 20px;
  }
  h1{
    color:#1a1a2e;
    font-size:30px;
  }
  p{
    color:#444;
    font-size:16px;
    max-width:500px;
    margin:15px auto 25px auto;
    line-height:1.5;
  }
  .pic{
    border:4px solid #1a1a2e;
    border-radius:8px;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

  <h1>Welcome to My Webpage</h1>
  <p>This page was made using basic HTML and CSS to practice page layout, text formatting and adding an image.</p>

  <svg class="pic" width="280" height="180" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
    <rect width="280" height="180" fill="#a3d2ff"/>
    <circle cx="220" cy="40" r="20" fill="#ffe066"/>
    <polygon points="0,180 70,90 140,180" fill="#3a7d44"/>
    <polygon points="90,180 160,70 240,180" fill="#2e5e34"/>
  </svg>

</body>
</html>
